# src/Makevars.win -- Windows-specific compiler hardening for evaluatr
#
# Same intent as Makevars (Unix). On Windows/MinGW-w64:
# -fvisibility=hidden  : restricts DLL export table to Rcpp-exported entry points only.
# -O2                  : release-mode optimisations.
# -DNDEBUG             : disables debug-build paths.
PKG_CXXFLAGS = -O2 -fvisibility=hidden -DNDEBUG
